HEADWORD: Niggardliness
<hw>Nig"gard*li*ness</hw> <pr>(n⟦icr⟧g"g⟦etil⟧rd*l⟦icr⟧*n⟦ecr⟧s)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being niggard; meanness in
